Tailscale（VPN）構築
raspberry piのbushにて以下を順番に入れる
1
sudo mkdir -p /etc/apt/keyrings

2
curl -fsSL https://pkgs.tailscale.com/stable/raspbian/buster.gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/tailscale-archive-keyring.gpg

3
echo "deb [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/tailscale-archive-keyring.gpg] https://pkgs.tailscale.com/stable/raspbian buster main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/tailscale.list

4
sudo apt update

5
sudo apt install tailscale

6
sudo tailscale up


1,2,3,4,5,6を順番に入力後以下のこうな文章がでてくる
To authenticate, visit:
https://login.tailscale.com/a/xxxxxxxxxxxx  <-- このURLをコピー


tailscaleのシステム停止方法と再起動方法

sudo systemctl stop tailscaled　停止

sudo systemctl start tailscaled　再起動
